  <summary date="2022-08-16T10:16:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Public Safety Enhancement Act of 2021

This bill reauthorizes through FY2026 the Community Oriented Policing Services (COPS) grant program.

Additionally, the bill requires a certain amount of funds made available under the COPS grant program to be used for the hiring and retention of law enforcement officers.</summary>
